OL,3,CIran executes three men detained
OL,4,Cduring nationwide protests
OL,6,FThree men detained in protests held
OL,7,Facross Iran in January have been
OL,8,Fexecuted, the country's judiciary has
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FThe executions of Mehdi Ghasemi, Saleh
OL,12,FMohammadi and Saeed Davvodi are the
OL,13,Ffirst such sentences known to have
OL,14,Fbeen carried out in relation to the
OL,15,Fdemonstrations.
OL,17,FThe three men allegedly stabbed two
OL,18,Fpolice officers to death in Qom, some
OL,19,F80 miles south of the capital, Tehran,
OL,20,Fduring the protests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
