OL,3,CIran executes three men detained
OL,4,Cduring nationwide protests
OL,6,FDemonstrations spread across the
OL,7,Fcountry in January this year amid
OL,8,Fpublic anger over the currency,
OL,9,FIranian rial, depreciating to new lows
OL,10,Fwhile inflationary pressures pushed up
OL,11,Fthe price of food and other every day
OL,12,Fessentials.
OL,14,FUS, European and United Nations
OL,15,Fsanctions have also added to these
OL,16,Fcost pressures, adding to the
OL,17,Fdiscontent already felt by Iranians
OL,18,Funhappy life under Tehran's hardline
OL,19,Fregime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
