OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773958309
OL,3,CIran executes three men detained
OL,4,Cduring nationwide protests
OL,6,FAnother wave of protests swept the
OL,7,Fcountry in September 2022 following
OL,8,Fthe death of 22-year-old Mahsa Amini
OL,9,Fwhile in police custody for violating
OL,10,Fthe country's strictly-enforced
OL,11,FIslamic dress code.
OL,13,FOf the most recent protests, Iran's
OL,14,Fjudiciary had threatened to carry out
OL,15,Fexecutions of those arrested in the
OL,16,Fdemonstrators. Iran typically carries
OL,17,Fout the death penalty with hangings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
