OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773958309
OL,3,CIran executes three men detained
OL,4,Cduring nationwide protests
OL,6,FIranian police have killed thousands
OL,7,Fof protesters in the streets and have
OL,8,Fdetained tens of thousands more, with
OL,9,Factivists warning of a potential wave
OL,10,Fof executions of those in detention.
OL,12,FIran has long been accused by rights
OL,13,Fcampaigners of forcing confessions
OL,14,Ffrom detainees and not allowing them
OL,15,Fto fully defend themselves in court.
OL,17,FIn January Trump threatened to take
OL,18,F"take very strong action" if Iranian
OL,19,Fauthorities started hanging anti-
OL,20,Fgovernment protesters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
