OL,3,CIran executes three men detained
OL,4,Cduring nationwide protests
OL,6,FThese threats appear redundant now,
OL,7,Fhowever, after the US and Israel
OL,8,Flaunched what they described as "pre-
OL,9,Femptive" strikes on 28 February on an
OL,10,FIran they viewed as intent on
OL,11,Facquiring nuclear weapons ` a claim
OL,12,FTehran denies.
OL,14,FThe war has since spilled out into the
OL,15,Fwider Middle East region, with Tehran
OL,16,Flaunching attacks on several oil-rich
OL,17,FGulf states allied with the US and
OL,18,Feffectively blockading the crucial
OL,19,Fshipping channel of the Strait of
OL,20,FHormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
